To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MorningDojiStar _morningdojistar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_morningdojistar = MorningDojiStar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_morningdojistar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "morningdojistar", _morningdojistar.Current.Value);
}
